name: mixed_safx75
source:
def mixed_safx75(x, y):
    t1 = jnp.tanh(x)
    t2 = t1 - y
    t3 = jnp.mean(t2)
    return t3
jaxpr:

    c:f32[4] = tanh a
    d:f32[4] = sub c b
    e:f32[] = reduce_sum[axes=(0,) out_sharding=None] d
    f:f32[] = div e 4.0:f32[]
  in (f,) }
